http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/bangalore/Group-of-20-people-stung-by-bees/article14021319.ece

A swarm of bees attacked around 20 people who had gone to perform the last rites of their relative in a field on the outskirts of Haridasanahalli in Turuvekere taluk of Tumakuru district on Tuesday.They took treatment in a hospital and were discharged later.